{"tid":1452094,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"連登係咪有內鬼?仲要成功左","createTime":"2019-08-11T23:51:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T23:59:41.000Z","uid":297244,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1278548a54a3a84222101e41f8496c6a0b2bd519","tid":1452094,"uid":297244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:51:42.000Z","msg":"大家不嬲Be water, 一個都不能少<br />\n8.11尋日下就連登有個post<br />\n用左好大段野去屌d人淨係識跑<br />\n見到警察就走 無撚用<br />\n<br />\n我初初見到都好奇怪 有少少嬲，我以為大家改左策略<br />\n有人留言問唔跑既話樓主有咩plan, 樓主一路無plan<br />\n<br />\n個post仲要比人推左上熱門.....<br />\n<br />\n到左夜晚我比一大堆新聞震撼一論<br />\n醒起有呢個post,<br />\n我即刻開返連登 已經搵唔返個post<br />\n最衰無cap圖又無share過出去<br />\n<br />\n經歷左尋晚<br />\n我只希望大家平平安安, 留得青山在<br />\n小心求證所有消息<br />\n<br />\n我第一次出post, 因為呢件事好似唔多人講"},{"pid":"4ae7152ea16f10177457d49751286a121b407d1d","tid":1452094,"uid":297244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:51:52.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"cbb74f68a3787c4fca4b0ec99ada0672e9ee08c3","tid":1452094,"uid":297244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:52:08.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2be2fcc31d5b81a81d59d03f1eee0b469ab3c13b","tid":1452094,"uid":297244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:53:33.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ee0efdb472870ea6809719e431631d29149298ae","tid":1452094,"uid":297244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:54:17.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"38da0cc89ce44159dcc827a2b900a67cccce681a","tid":1452094,"uid":297244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:54:50.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"355ac6574c8f1516f205d1d7cde54db3c5ad8f8c","tid":1452094,"uid":297244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:55:49.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c258a90913bd798fd04d104b43bf63fe3a121e50","tid":1452094,"uid":297244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:56:32.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"86290bac0207e27a8